org.amv.trafficsoft.rest.client

Interface ClientConfig<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the client this class is configuring
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClientConfig.ConfigurableClientConfig

    public interface ClientConfig<T>
    A configuration interface for clients.

    The user of this interface has precise control over how a client class behaves internally and is able to configure it to his needs.
